title: SID music: Jeroen Tel - Cybernoid II (Title) (U64E real 6581 dual mono bx_🎧)
description:

title: SID music: Jeroen Tel - Myth (Title) (FPGASID 6581 dual mono bx_🎧)
description:
"Myth: History in the Making" (C64, 1989) title theme by Jeroen Tel.

Made using FPGASID fw 0A. 2 x 6581 in dual mono. Left bias -3, right bias -4.
